title: Fokker C-31A Troopship
content:
@ Joint Base Andrews, Maryland

May 2011

Taken during my first trip to the Andrews Joint Service Open House airshow.  The US Army Golden Knights parachute demonstration team jumpship passes overhead after takeoff.  The Troopship is the military version of the F27-400 Friendship and has been used by the Golden Knights since 1985.  Nikon D300 w/ 300mm, processing with Aperture.
